data.meta_description: Feb 10, 2022 - Leona Lewis (born 3 April 1985) is a British singer, songwriter, actress, model. Lewis , winning a Â£1 million recording contract with Syco Music. Her winner's single, a cover of Kelly Clarkson's "A Moment Like This", peaked at number one for four weeks on the UK Singles Chart and broke a world record by reaching 50,000 digital downloads within 30 minutes. In February 2007, Lewis signed a five-album contract in the United States with Clive Davis's record label, J Records. See more ideas about leona lewis, lewis, syco music.
